      "span_text": "Particularly, for the Lab MBR bioreactor, which stands as a highly enriched (>90%)  culture of Brocadiales, the relative abundance found was 1.27% when 44 ∘ C was the annealing temperature, while at the other temperatures assayed it fell in the 75-86% range."
